<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>로그인 - ECO-LIFE Mall</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #064E3B;
            --primary-hover: #064E3B;
            --bg-color: #f8fafc;
            --text-dark: #1e293b;
            --text-gray: #64748b;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .login-container {
            background: white;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .back-to-home {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: var(--text-gray);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        .back-to-home:hover {
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        h2 {
            color: var(--text-dark);
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .input-group {
            text-align: left;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .input-group label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.85em;
            color: var(--text-gray);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            margin-left: 4px;
        }

        input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--primary-color);
            background-color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1);
        }

        button {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            padding: 16px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 10px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: var(--primary-hover);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.3);
        }

        button:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .find-links {
            margin-top: 25px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .find-links a {
            font-size: 0.85em;
            color: var(--text-gray);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        .find-links a:hover {
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        .register-prompt {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: var(--text-gray);
        }

        .register-prompt a {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="login-container">
        <a href="../" class="back-to-home">🏠 홈으로 돌아가기</a>
        
        <h2>로그인</h2>
        
        <form action="/user/login" method="post">
            <div class="input-group">
                <label>아이디</label>
                <input type="text" name="username" placeholder="아이디를 입력하세요" required>
            </div>
            
            <div class="input-group">
                <label>비밀번호</label>
                <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="비밀번호를 입력하세요" required>
            </div>
            
            <button type="submit">로그인</button>
        </form>

        <div class="find-links">
            <a href="./user/find-id">아이디 찾기</a>
            <span style="color: #e2e8f0;">|</span>
            <a href="./user/find-pw">비밀번호 찾기</a>
        </div>

        <div class="register-prompt">
            아직 회원이 아니신가요? <a href="./user/register">회원가입</a>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>